2014", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7181.html", target="_top", tooltip="This specification describes version 2 of the Optimized Link State Routing Protocol (OLSRv2) for Mobile Ad Hoc Networks (MANETs)."];
  cites -> RFC7181;
  RFC6507 [label="RFC6507
Elliptic Curve-Based Certificateless
Signatures for Identity-Based Encryption
(ECCSI)
2012", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC6507.html", target="_top", tooltip="Many signature schemes currently in use rely on certificates for authentication of identity.  In Identity-based cryptography, this adds unnecessary overhead and administration.  The Elliptic Curve-based Certificateless Signatures for Identity-based Encryption (ECCSI) signature scheme described in this document is certificateless.  This scheme has the additional advantages of low bandwidth and low computational requirements.  This document is not an Internet Standards Track specification; it is published for informational purposes."];
  cites -> RFC6507;
  RFC2119 [label="RFC2119
Key words for use in RFCs to Indicate
Requirement Levels
1997", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC2119.html", target="_top", tooltip="In many standards track documents several words are used to signify the requirements in the specification.  These words are often capitalized.  This document defines these words as they should be interpreted in IETF documents.  This document specifies an Internet Best Current Practices for the Internet Community, and requests discussion and suggestions for improvements."];
  cites -> RFC2119;
